      "type": "text",
      "x": 430,
      "y": 422,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 72,
      "text": "Key Status Codes:\n2xx Success: 200 OK, 201 Created, 204 No Content\n3xx Redirect: 301 Permanent, 302 Temporary, 304 Not Modified\n4xx Client: 400, 401 Unauth, 403 Forbidden, 404, 429 Rate Limited\n5xx Server: 500, 502 Bad Gateway, 503 Unavailable",
      "fontSize": 12,
